OS/2 executables for PGP 2.2 are available from

	ftp.uni-erlangen.de, pub/pc/os2/fauern/crypt/pgp22os2.zip

The archive contains 16-bit (OS/2 1.x) and 32-bit (OS/2 2.x)
executables. The 16-bit one runs under OS/2 2.x and even under plain
DOS as well, while the 32-bit one runs under OS/2 2.x only.

I did not do too extensive testing (due to lack of time at the moment)
but it seems to function normally.

Kai Uwe Rommel

